description: NaanSense is an Indian food truck serving the streets of Seattle, The East Side, and other parts of King County. The goal of this truck is to offer a modern, comfortable approach to Indian cuisine while keeping traditional roots and offering it all at affordable prices. Menu items can include Butter Chicken, Saag Paneer, Lamb Vindaloo, Stuffed Eggplant, Roasted Bitter Melon, Kohlrabi Dahl, Ghee Basmati Rice, and, of course, the eponymous Naan. Check out this amazing, fresh, handmade naan, and all the other delicious food this truck has to offer!
name: NaanSense
